data.description: No More showings After Sunday 2/18/24  . Seller has multiple offers and will make a decision on Monday 2/19/23    🏡 Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 5-bed, 2-bath Brick Cape Cod residence is about to make its debut on the market, and you won't want to miss the opportunity to call it yours.  Step inside to discover a kitchen that's been completely updated and transformed into a modern culinary haven. The sleek design features a convenient island, brand new stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and elegant tile floors. Enjoy seamless indoor-outdoor living with direct access to the back patio right from the kitchen—a perfect spot for entertaining or relaxing with a cup of coffee. Note: Floors were all redone picture doesn't reflect that. They look amazing !    Both bathrooms have undergone a chic and contemporary makeover, providing a luxurious experience. The first floor boasts two bedrooms with ceiling fans and a full bath, all tastefully updated. Ascend to the second floor, where three more bedrooms await, accompanied by another updated and modern bath.  Gorgeous hardwood floors grace every inch of this home, recently refinished to perfection. The result is a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout .Also, enjoy the convenience of  first floor laundry.  Need additional space? The full, unfinished walkout basement offers endless possibilities for customization to suit your needs.  Outdoor living is a breeze with a fenced yard, providing privacy and security, along with a utility shed for added convenience. Picture yourself enjoying the fresh air on the back patio, creating memories in your own little oasis.  With a private driveway and all these incredible features, this home is a rare find. Don't miss your chance to make it yours—schedule your showing today and consider yourself lucky to call this remarkable property "home." Act swiftly, as opportunities like this don't last long! 🏡✨ This Home is Protected with a 1 Year AHS Home Warranty !
